package model
  • Class
    Description
    Bullet
    The Bullet class represents a projectile shot by a Peashooter.
    CandidateIcePeashooter
    The CandidateIcePeashooter class represents a candidate ice peashooter that can be placed in the game but does not move or shoot bullets.
    CandidatePeashooter
    The CandidatePeashooter class represents a candidate peashooter that can be placed in the game but does not move or shoot bullets.
    CommandCenter
    The CommandCenter class manages the state of the game, including the player's resources, plants, zombies, bullets, and game levels.
    CrazyZombie
    The CrazyZombie class represents a special type of zombie with unique characteristics such as swinging legs, variable speed, and the ability to be frozen by ice bullets.
    ExplodingHead
    The ExplodingHead class represents the animated explosion effect of a zombie's head.
    IcePeashooter
    The IcePeashooter class represents a specialized type of Peashooter that shoots ice bullets.
    LevelInstruction
    The LevelInstruction class represents an on-screen message displayed to inform the player about the current level or important events.
    Movable
    The Movable interface represents any object in the game that can move, be drawn, detect collisions, and expire.
    Peashooter
    The Peashooter class represents a plant that shoots bullets at zombies.
    Sound
    The Sound class handles audio playback for the game, including playing individual sounds and looping audio clips.
    Sprite
    The Sprite class represents a movable and drawable object in the game.
    Sun
    Represents a Sun object in the game.
    Tuple
    Represents a tuple that holds a list of movable objects and a specific target object.
    Zombie
    Represents a Zombie character in the game.
